If You Want More Extra Themes
Command
sudo apt update
sudo apt install plymouth-themes
If you want spinner theme
sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/Triaxis-logo.png /usr/share/plymouth/themes/spinner/watermark.png
sudo update-initramfs -u
if you want to change bgrt fallback here
sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/triaxis-logo.png /usr/share/plymouth/themes/spinner/bgrt-fallback.png
sudo update-initramfs -u
If you want to set a theme you want
sudo update-alternatives --config default.plymouth
/usr/share/plymouth/themes/yourtheme/yourtheme.plymouth
Example
/usr/share/plymouth/themes/spinner/spinner.plymouth
For Breeze
sudo apt install plymouth-theme-breeze
Then sudo nano /usr/share/plymouth/themes/breeze-text/breeze-text.plymouth
then change title to Triaxis GNU/Linux Rolling Release _________ For Example Triaxis GNU/Linux Rolling Release 2026.1.08
Then sudo update-initramfs -u
Then reboot
If you Want To add plymouth themes use
sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/share/plymouth/themes/default.plymouth default.plymouth /usr/share/plymouth/themes/<theme-name>/<theme-name>.plymouth 100
For The Spinfinity
sudo cp /usr/share/pixmaps/triaxis-logo.png /usr/share/plymouth/themes/spinfinity/header-image.png
sudo update-initramfs -u

To Change plymouth theme Logo Using sudo cp or sudo mv dont forget to use sudo update-initramfs -u

Warning Some Text On Plymouth Themes Name Text With 4 Dots and Breeze-Text Might Have Different Fonts
